[background arg="res://assets/narrative/checkpoint_corridor.png" fade="0.0"]
join narrator [z_index="1"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: The border facility feels different today. Tense. Security patrols in greater numbers as wary silence replaces chatter.
